  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of AMN107 in Patients With GastroIntestinal Stromal Tumors (GIST) Who Have Failed Both Imatinib and Sunitinib</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center Phase II Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of AMN107 (Nilotinib) in Patients With Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumors Who Have Progressed on or Are Intolerant to Both Imatinib and Sunitinib</official_title>
